responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "16A2C6F24B47DAD125E782B783B7C0DB", "Not this one. We can\'t just be tapping into the essence for picking flowers. Only the lineage members of the Legion of the Rose have a finer crown. But this one will no doubt open a few doors or in the least garner an ale or two. ")
